title: ADD_MINIMAP_OVERLAY_WITH_DEPTH
content:
0xED0935B5// AddMinimapOverlayWithDepth
int ADD_MINIMAP_OVERLAY_WITH_DEPTH(char* name, int depth);Parameters:name: The path to a .gfx file in the current resource. It has to be specified as a file.depth: The depth of new overlay on the minimap. Pass -1 for game to figure out the highest depth itself. Should not be greater than 0x7EFFFFFD.Returns: A minimap overlay ID.Loads a minimap overlay from a GFx file in the current resource.
